1. Added Quick Chat function. Enter a channel and chat with your favorite streamers with just one click!
2. Added the floating window playback function. You can now continue watching live-streams after exiting the live-stream room. Continue your viewing experience uninterrupted!
3. Character limit per message in the chat room increased to 100;
4. Optimized the share function - removed the large image covering the screen after a screenshot;
5. Follow function added to "History"

